executionArgs.additionalInstruction: The backend uses FastAPI running on port 8000. Auth endpoints: POST /register, POST /login, POST /logout, GET /me. Image endpoints: POST /images (multipart upload), POST /images/{image_id}/transform, GET /images/{image_id}, DELETE /images/{image_id}. IMPORTANT: image_id is an INTEGER (not UUID). All image endpoints require Bearer token authentication. Register first to get a token. Register body: {username, password, email}. Login body: {username, password, remember_me}. For image upload use multipart form data with field 'file'. Use integer IDs when referencing images (e.g. 1, 2, 999999 for non-existent).
